{"tid":260872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得我一個覺得柯潔好可憐 （2）","createTime":"2017-05-28T04:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T14:39:00.000Z","uid":41818,"like":11,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"490cc73110d0b57d60cc02334ab36866579a7bb1","tid":260872,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論，當你做到世界第一嗰陣，見到身邊好多實力同自己相近既高手全部都輸比一個AI，比著你都會唔服，都會想代替人類贏一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我亦都唔會否認佢係賽前既言論係偏激同串左少少，但作為人類最後希望既時候，唔通仲要講D咩alphago好勁，我應該唔會贏之類既晦氣說話咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n站係棋手既立場，如果alphago贏左柯潔，即係代表人類研究圍棋幾千年既歷史都不如一個21世紀既AI程式，旁人睇可能冇乜野，但如果你係真正熱愛圍棋既話，我諗心入面都唔會好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講，佢輸左之後亦都大方承認係自己棋藝不足，而冇好似鄭智咁周圍搵藉口黎掩飾自己既失敗，作為世界第一而且年紀咁細，我認為佢已經好得體大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「這局棋後，AlphaGo在我眼裡十全十美，對我來說，它就是圍棋上帝，」<br />\n「對人類來說，我們對圍棋的認識非常有限。」<br />\n唔好話我睇死你地，你地之所以會不斷話柯潔串只不過係因為佢係支那人，如果係其他國家一定話佢好型呀又乜又物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果連登仔真係做到咁對人唔對事既話，我亦都冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">各位屌細力D</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"de3d01a97ad7f78804eb8abee1ebb813a31b41dc","tid":260872,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/260178/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/260178/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\npost 1"},{"pid":"dad62cca6b0717d5f308984052cb2c49b1457d9f","tid":260872,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n所以話, 中國人既性格真係天生臭串<br />\n我先講一講我既經歷<br />\n<br />\n我以前讀小學四年級, 數學全班第一, 83分<br />\n老師叫我發表感受<br />\n<br />\n我都話:「我唔會因為咁就驕傲, 我會繼續努力, 去到100分」<br />\n結果我獲得全班掌聲, 連老師都親毛讚揚我 勝不驕 既精神<br />\n<br />\n事實證明, 19歲柯潔 係人格上,  連我小學四年級果陣都不如</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8fc3f231e43ccc5c9f3461ab01662bcf91ff26fc","tid":260872,"uid":51152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"真係好懷疑盲撐同盲反都有五毛喺度扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fd8b763b7c16f8af8d9ba34cce44a9a5e809ab","tid":260872,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d874c14e4c5ec71324676374c2691a93aeabe74b","tid":260872,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"正反雙方立論均已附上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c6371aff44bd718627ca7417d7dd6a380da041","tid":260872,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"點解咁都開到post2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a755a74a985ea68424fff8a486bcfdf26ca338","tid":260872,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"遲d應該會有個相反立場嘅post呃正評"},{"pid":"2a614be53690f5710a44aedc1e02d5b9acb886ce","tid":260872,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲d應該會有個相反立場嘅post呃正評</blockquote><br />\n而家出面已經大撚把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec840dc067295b941e3c5e4071947c9d0c645fa4","tid":26